title: Evening at Visapur dam
description: Visapur Dam, is an earthfill dam on Hanga river near Srigonda, Ahmednagar district in the state of Maharashtra in India. It is Very Old Dam & is developed by British government in 1905. Now this dam is included in kukdi prakalp & this dam is used to provide Water to the Farms

title: Monsoon and Beautiful Location
description: Talegaon Dabhade is a town in Mawal Taluka, Pune district, in the Indian state of Maharashtra. It is 120 km from Mumbai and 35 km from Pune.
